Class AVInputFormat53

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bridj.NativeObject

        • org.libav.avformat.bridge.AVInputFormat53
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NativeObjectInterface

    public class AVInputFormat53
extends StructObject
    Mirror of the native AVInputFormat struct for the libavformat v53.x.x. For details see the Libav documentation.
    Author:
    Ondrej Perutka
